<SYNC Start=397940><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=400067><P Class=KRCC>예감이 좋아
<SYNC Start=401777><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=401860><P Class=KRCC>그래?
<SYNC Start=402861><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=404488><P Class=KRCC>로리가 샘플을<br>가져올 거야
<SYNC Start=406031><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=406156><P Class=KRCC>그래야지
<SYNC Start=407741><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=410661><P Class=KRCC>경로 수정 준비
