<SYNC Start=457040><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=457708><P Class=KRCC><i>난 재밌는데<br>다들 재밌어?</i>
<SYNC Start=459543><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=459668><P Class=KRCC>로리
<SYNC Start=460711><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=460794><P Class=KRCC>- 만약 놓치면 ...<br>- <i>알아, 알아</i>
<SYNC Start=462713><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=462796><P Class=KRCC>놓쳤다간...
