<SYNC Start=2697112><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2703493><P Class=KRCC><i>분당 심박 61<br>혈압 97/53</i>
<SYNC Start=2708039><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2708957><P Class=KRCC><i>너무 느긋하신데요?</i>
<SYNC Start=2710875><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=2710959><P Class=KRCC><i>침착하신 거지<br>안 그래요?</i>
<SYNC Start=2713503><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
